 well (e.g.
 marriage).
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
Asset ownership
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Other than projecting their status through higher priced items, but consumers
 also wish to associate themselves to those who they perceive to have a
 higher status.
 Acquiring long-term assets are surest way to ascertain one's status in
 society
