\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The consumption of a lot status items could be dependent on each other -
 i.e.
 the status disadvantage from not consuming an item 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 may add up towards the disadvantage from not consuming 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 if the consumption on 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

