LatexCommand cite
key "DeatonEconConsumer"

\end_inset

.
 The second solution is the Gorman polar form where the indirect utility
 function takes the form 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{G}(\frac{x_{G}}{b_{G}(p_{G})})+a_{G}(p_{G})$
\end_inset

