 For example, if only city-dwellers enjoy a certain amenity - then moving
 to the city would be factored in by 
\begin_inset Formula $\Pi$
\end_inset

.
 If consumers of a different personal characteristic 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho_{k}$
\end_inset

